text: GoIF Fram is a sports club in the town of Jönköping in Sweden. It was established in 1921. It played in the Swedish men's handball top division during the 1939-1940 season. The club later became more focused on bowling. The bowling section was established on 1 april 1960. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website Category:1921 establishments in Sweden Category:Handball clubs in Sweden Category:Sport in Jönköping
